Chissà, <delay8 />forse se fossi un granchio...
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />AHAHAH!<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="400" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Beh<tag a="110" b="0" /> <delay8 />perché sei tu, <delay8 />posso farti
un prezzone<tag a="110" b="0" /> <tag a="90" b="21" arg="0x3" />,
<delay8 />per esempio. <delay20 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ti va bene?</message>
	<message label="400_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">Sì!</message>
	<message label="400_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Scenderesti un po'?</message>
	<message label="401" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Troppo forte, grazie! <delay20 />Affare fatto!</message>
	<message label="402" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Cavoli, <delay8 />mi hai dato un grande aiuto,
<tag a="110" b="6" />.</message>
	<message label="403" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Ah, <delay8 />sei un osso duro, eh? <delay20 />Ti stimo.
