Va bene ora<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />?</message>
	<message label="404_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">Sì!</message>
	<message label="404_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Dai, abbassa il prezzo!</message>
	<message label="405" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Argh! <delay8 />Al mio capo non piacerà<tag a="110" b="0" />
